Package net.sourceforge.fastupload

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ContentHeaderMap
    Represent headers of a boundary of multipart/form-data input stream.
    FastUploadParser
    Refer to RFC1867, High level API for multipart/form-data ServletInputStream parsing.
    FileFactory
    A factory that indicate which concrete sub class of MultiPart to be created.
    MemoryMultiPart
    parse the bytes of multipart data, read those bytes into a buffer, also the StreamMultipartFile object contains headers of multipart data
    MemoryUploadParser
    Concrete class of UploadParser that implements main parseList() function that return List<MultiPart> The class read all bytes from ServletInputStream before parse it, which behavior is not as same as StreamUploadParser
    MultiPart
    Abstract class represent content between two boundary, called a MultiPart, refer to RFC1867.
    MultiPartBinaryFile
    A concrete class of MultiPartDiskFile.
    MultiPartDiskFile
    A abstract sub class of MultiPart.
    MultiPartTextFile
    The class represent a boundary data is binary file.
    ProgressListener
    progress listener of FastUploadParser parsing bytes from ServletInputSteam
    StreamUploadParser
    A concrete class of UploadParser that override parseList() function.
    UploadParser
    Abstract class defines basic structure of parsing multipart/form-data input stream.
